{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/2019-10-08-react/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0375d465-04d4-5e5d-a59d-c3d68e50ad4f","html":"<h2 id=\"react-란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#react-%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"react 란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://ko.reactjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">React 란?</a></h2>\n<p>페이스북과 인스타그램으로 유명한 페이스북에서 만든 <strong>UI 라이브러리</strong>입니다.\n리액트는 다른 모던 웹 기술과는 다르게 프레임워크라고는 하지 않고 <strong>라이브러리</strong>라고 하는데요.\n이는 리액트는 <strong>기본적으로 컴포넌트를 통한 화면 표현만을 담당</strong>하기 때문입니다. 리액트에는 웹을 개발하는데 꼭 필요한 기본적인 구성요소들이 포함되어 있지 않습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"웹-개발-시-필요한-추가-라이브러리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%EC%8B%9C-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"웹 개발 시 필요한 추가 라이브러리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>웹 개발 시, 필요한 추가 라이브러리</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>React-Router … (페이지 라우팅)</li>\n<li>Redux, MobX … (데이터 상태 관리)</li>\n<li>Redux-Saga, Redux-Thunk … (네트워크 및 비동기 데이터 처리)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"그외\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8%EC%99%B8\" aria-label=\"그외 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>그외</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>ECMAScript 6+ 문법</li>\n<li>Component Base Development (CBD) 개발 방법론</li>\n<li>Webpack</li>\n<li>Babel</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"create-react-app\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#create-react-app\" aria-label=\"create react app permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://create-react-app.dev/docs/getting-started\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Create-React-App</a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/d76ab/react-create-react-app.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/8ac56/react-create-react-app.webp 240w,\n/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/d3be9/react-create-react-app.webp 480w,\n/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/e46b2/react-create-react-app.webp 960w,\n/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/f992d/react-create-react-app.webp 1440w,\n/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/b8c25/react-create-react-app.webp 1731w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/8ff5a/react-create-react-app.png 240w,\n/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/e85cb/react-create-react-app.png 480w,\n/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/d9199/react-create-react-app.png 960w,\n/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/07a9c/react-create-react-app.png 1440w,\n/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/d76ab/react-create-react-app.png 1731w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ff0d9178b53bc90d672f94cade59851f/d9199/react-create-react-app.png\"\n            alt=\"image.png\"\n            title=\"image.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>처음 리액트를 시작할 때, 유용한 Create React App 패키지입니다.</strong>\nFacebook에서 제공하는 패키지로 개발용 Node 서버 및 Webpack, Babel 설정 등 리액트를 개발하는데 있어 필요한 기본 설정이 포함되어 있습니다.</p>\n<p>Create-React-App으로 개발 시 <strong>SPA(Single-Page-Application)</strong> 구조를 갖습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"jsx-문법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#jsx-%EB%AC%B8%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"jsx 문법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>JSX 문법</h2>\n<p>리액트에서 화면을 구성하는 문법중 하나인 자바스크립트 xml입니다.</p>\n<p>Facebook에서 만들었고 XHP라는 언어가 기반이 되었다고 합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 570px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/05d660bd5a23e0cdcdbcb188e40dad7f/432e7/react-jsx-01.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/05d660bd5a23e0cdcdbcb188e40dad7f/8ac56/react-jsx-01.webp 240w,\n/static/05d660bd5a23e0cdcdbcb188e40dad7f/d3be9/react-jsx-01.webp 480w,\n/static/05d660bd5a23e0cdcdbcb188e40dad7f/048c8/react-jsx-01.webp 570w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/05d660bd5a23e0cdcdbcb188e40dad7f/8ff5a/react-jsx-01.png 240w,\n/static/05d660bd5a23e0cdcdbcb188e40dad7f/e85cb/react-jsx-01.png 480w,\n/static/05d660bd5a23e0cdcdbcb188e40dad7f/432e7/react-jsx-01.png 570w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/05d660bd5a23e0cdcdbcb188e40dad7f/432e7/react-jsx-01.png\"\n            alt=\"image.png\"\n            title=\"image.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위의 이미지가 JSX 문법으로 된 화면입니다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 570px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/121716a5350f47314a53fca58ab14c70/432e7/react-jsx-02.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/121716a5350f47314a53fca58ab14c70/8ac56/react-jsx-02.webp 240w,\n/static/121716a5350f47314a53fca58ab14c70/d3be9/react-jsx-02.webp 480w,\n/static/121716a5350f47314a53fca58ab14c70/048c8/react-jsx-02.webp 570w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/121716a5350f47314a53fca58ab14c70/8ff5a/react-jsx-02.png 240w,\n/static/121716a5350f47314a53fca58ab14c70/e85cb/react-jsx-02.png 480w,\n/static/121716a5350f47314a53fca58ab14c70/432e7/react-jsx-02.png 570w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/121716a5350f47314a53fca58ab14c70/432e7/react-jsx-02.png\"\n            alt=\"image.png\"\n            title=\"image.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 자바스크립트로 구성한 화면입니다.</p>\n<p>대체로 첫번째 이미지의 JSX 문법을 이용한 구성이 익숙해지면 가독성이 더 좋다고 생각합니다.</p>\n<p><strong>리액트에서 JSX 문법을 사용하려면 Babel을 이용한 트랜스파일링이 필요합니다.</strong></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"spa-single-page-application\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spa-single-page-application\" aria-label=\"spa single page application permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPA (Single Page Application)</h2>\n<p>Create-React-App으로 프로젝트를 생성하면,\nSPA(Single Page Application)으로 생성되며 하나의 html 문서에 javascript 코드로 내부 가상 돔(Virtual DOM)을 조작하여 화면을 표시합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/37ef91c262f327844f914b454364a173/1cfc2/react-spa-01.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/37ef91c262f327844f914b454364a173/8ac56/react-spa-01.webp 240w,\n/static/37ef91c262f327844f914b454364a173/d3be9/react-spa-01.webp 480w,\n/static/37ef91c262f327844f914b454364a173/131f1/react-spa-01.webp 900w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/37ef91c262f327844f914b454364a173/8ff5a/react-spa-01.png 240w,\n/static/37ef91c262f327844f914b454364a173/e85cb/react-spa-01.png 480w,\n/static/37ef91c262f327844f914b454364a173/1cfc2/react-spa-01.png 900w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/37ef91c262f327844f914b454364a173/1cfc2/react-spa-01.png\"\n            alt=\"image.png\"\n            title=\"image.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위의 이미지를 보시면 root라는 id를 가진 엘리먼트에 App이라는 컴포넌트를 렌더링하여 화면에 표시하도록 되어있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/657a474a55b5767c7970331690ee3729/8c557/react-spa-02.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.16666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/657a474a55b5767c7970331690ee3729/8ac56/react-spa-02.webp 240w,\n/static/657a474a55b5767c7970331690ee3729/d3be9/react-spa-02.webp 480w,\n/static/657a474a55b5767c7970331690ee3729/426ac/react-spa-02.webp 700w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/657a474a55b5767c7970331690ee3729/8ff5a/react-spa-02.png 240w,\n/static/657a474a55b5767c7970331690ee3729/e85cb/react-spa-02.png 480w,\n/static/657a474a55b5767c7970331690ee3729/8c557/react-spa-02.png 700w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/657a474a55b5767c7970331690ee3729/8c557/react-spa-02.png\"\n            alt=\"image.png\"\n            title=\"image.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\">App은 위의 이미지처럼 컴포넌트로 구성 되어있고 실행하면 다음과 같이 나타납니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/428f986f4bd9fa7fb346432e81d3dad7/8c557/react-spa-03.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 114.16666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/428f986f4bd9fa7fb346432e81d3dad7/8ac56/react-spa-03.webp 240w,\n/static/428f986f4bd9fa7fb346432e81d3dad7/d3be9/react-spa-03.webp 480w,\n/static/428f986f4bd9fa7fb346432e81d3dad7/426ac/react-spa-03.webp 700w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/428f986f4bd9fa7fb346432e81d3dad7/8ff5a/react-spa-03.png 240w,\n/static/428f986f4bd9fa7fb346432e81d3dad7/e85cb/react-spa-03.png 480w,\n/static/428f986f4bd9fa7fb346432e81d3dad7/8c557/react-spa-03.png 700w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/428f986f4bd9fa7fb346432e81d3dad7/8c557/react-spa-03.png\"\n            alt=\"image.png\"\n            title=\"image.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"state-props\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#state-props\" aria-label=\"state props permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>State, Props</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/23f9744d854cb93d0caee182fea73393/5a190/react-state-props.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 102.91666666666669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/23f9744d854cb93d0caee182fea73393/8ac56/react-state-props.webp 240w,\n/static/23f9744d854cb93d0caee182fea73393/d3be9/react-state-props.webp 480w,\n/static/23f9744d854cb93d0caee182fea73393/d00b9/react-state-props.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/23f9744d854cb93d0caee182fea73393/8ff5a/react-state-props.png 240w,\n/static/23f9744d854cb93d0caee182fea73393/e85cb/react-state-props.png 480w,\n/static/23f9744d854cb93d0caee182fea73393/5a190/react-state-props.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/23f9744d854cb93d0caee182fea73393/5a190/react-state-props.png\"\n            alt=\"image.png\"\n            title=\"image.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>리액트 컴포넌트의 경우 컴포넌트 내부에 <strong>state</strong>와 <strong>props</strong>라는 상태값을 가질수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><strong>다른 컴포넌트로부터 넘겨받는 상태값은 props로 들어오며,\n컴포넌트 내부의 상태값은 state로 구성할 수 있습니다.</strong></p>\n<p>해당 컴포넌트 외부로 상태값을 넘기고 싶을때는 callback 함수를 만들어서 외부에서 호출해주는 방식으로 구현해야 합니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"class-component-lifecycle\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#class-component-lifecycle\" aria-label=\"class component lifecycle permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Class Component LifeCycle</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/896c7/react-life-cycle.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/8ac56/react-life-cycle.webp 240w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/d3be9/react-life-cycle.webp 480w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/e46b2/react-life-cycle.webp 960w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/f992d/react-life-cycle.webp 1440w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/882b9/react-life-cycle.webp 1920w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/b07fc/react-life-cycle.webp 1938w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/8ff5a/react-life-cycle.png 240w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/e85cb/react-life-cycle.png 480w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/d9199/react-life-cycle.png 960w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/07a9c/react-life-cycle.png 1440w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/29114/react-life-cycle.png 1920w,\n/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/896c7/react-life-cycle.png 1938w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d02089f71e7f521781a455fb8c212634/d9199/react-life-cycle.png\"\n            alt=\"image.png\"\n            title=\"image.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>리액트 컴포넌트 생명 주기입니다.\n<strong>Props 또는 State 값이 변경되거나 컴포넌트가 마운트, 언마운트될때 호출됩니다.</strong></p>\n<p>Props나 State 값이 변경될때 화면의 Rendering이 다시 이뤄지며,\n랜더링이 필요하지 않을 경우에는</p>\n<p>생명주기의 Updation 부분에 포함된 메소드에서 return 값을 수정, 반환하면\n컴포넌트 랜더링이 다시 이뤄지지 않습니다.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2019-10-08-react/","tagSlugs":["/tag/frontend/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-10-08T13:00:00.121Z","description":"","tags":["Frontend"],"title":"[React] React?","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2019-10-08-react/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}